  {"name"=>"Fluffhead","name_lower"=>"fluffhead","link"=>"http://www.phish.net/song/fluffhead/lyrics","lyrics"=>"  fluffhead was a man with a horrible disease could not find no cure wont you help him if you please? fluff came to my door askin me for change his eyes were clear and pure but his mind was so deranged fluff went to a banker askin for some bills the banker said, i aint got that but i sure got some powerful pills. ","lyrics_by"=>"Anastasio/Pollak"},
  {"name"=>"Contact","name_lower"=>"contact","link"=>"http://www.phish.net/song/contact/lyrics","lyrics"=>"  the tires are the things on your car that make contact with the road the car is the thing on the road that takes you back to your abode the tires are the things on your car that make contact with the road bummed is what you are when you go out to your car and its been towed i woke up one morning in november and i realized i love you its not your headlights in front your tailpipe, or the skylight above you its the way you cling to the road when the wind tries to shove you id never go riding away and come back home without you ","lyrics_by"=>"Gordon"},
