  {"name"=>"Big Black Furry Creature from Mars","name_lower"=>"big black furry creature from mars","link"=>"http://www.phish.net/song/big-black-furry-creature-from-mars/lyrics","lyrics"=>"  when i get home from work, what do i do? i try to kill you when i get home from work, what do i do? i try to kill you and why would i try to kill you? because youre a big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars when we go out to eat, what do i do? i try to kill you when we go out to eat, what do i do? oh, i am killing you now why would i go and do that? because youre a big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars im runnin, im runnin from you im runnin, im runnin and what causes me to run? cause youre a big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars big black furry creature from mars ","lyrics_by"=>"Gordon"},
