  {"name"=>"Splinters of Hail","name_lower"=>"splinters of hail","link"=>"http://www.phish.net/song/splinters-of-hail/lyrics","lyrics"=>"  found the beauty of small things in this time, running free turned off notices feet are back on the ground in this time, came around ladders rising up and through these splinters of hail these blocks i built are keeping me from letting go pick up one see it put it aside turn around, around found the beauty of small things splinters of hail (splinters of hail) turn around splinters of hail (splinters of hail) ","lyrics_by"=>"Anastasio"},
  {"name"=>"Cant Come Back","name_lower"=>"cant come back","link"=>"http://www.phish.net/song/cant-come-back/lyrics","lyrics"=>"  one small step i saw you take along the tube toward the glow words i formed to call you back you paused and spoke soft and low cant come back cant come back i cant come back, come back i thought i saw you in your chair a shadow bent like you were there i asked the dark what would you think of coming back to join me cant come back cant come back i cant come back, come back cant go back cant go back i cant go back, go back ","lyrics_by"=>"Gordon"},
